: "Francis", "pid": 447431, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "中国佛教有很多自己的流派，藏传佛教、南传佛教、日本佛教和我们的都有较大差别", "timestamp": 1629683303, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 0, "pid": 447431, "reply": 9, "tag": null, "text": "佛教是外国传来的，它属于传统文化吗？", "timestamp": 1629679516, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1629683302, "url": "", "vote": {}}}